&lt;P align=left&gt;of Norrath had ever seen a werewolf. It&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P align=left&gt;wasn't until an expedition of Qeynosian miners&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P align=left&gt;breached the barrier of Darkhollow that the first&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P align=left&gt;werewolf was seen and the first human bitten.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
